  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no, the screen is black. It doesn't work. Come on, start. Please start.",
      "zh": "喔不，螢幕是黑的。它不工作。拜託，開機。請開機。",
      "ja": "ああ、画面が真っ黒だ。動かない。さあ、起動して。お願い、起動して。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nothing. No music. No messages. Oh, this is so bad.",
      "zh": "什麼都沒有。沒有音樂。沒有訊息。喔，這太糟了。",
      "ja": "何もない。音楽もない。メッセージもない。ああ、これはひどい。",
      "time": "00:00:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm, still no power. The phone is dead.",
      "zh": "嗯，還是沒電。手機死機了。",
      "ja": "うーん、まだ電源が入らない。携帯が死んでる。",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Morning, Emma. Why do you look so stressed?",
      "zh": "早安，Emma。你看起來很緊張，為什麼？",
      "ja": "おはよう、エマ。なんでそんなにストレスを感じているの？",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi, Anna. My phone is broken.",
      "zh": "嗨，Anna。我的手機壞了。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、アンナ。私の携帯が壊れたの。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look. The screen is black. It won't turn on.",
      "zh": "看。螢幕是黑的。它不會開機。",
      "ja": "見て。画面が真っ黒で、起動しないの。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, that's sad. Did you charge it?",
      "zh": "喔，那很可惜。你有充電嗎？",
      "ja": "ああ、それは残念ね。充電した？",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, I tried. No light. No sound. Nothing.",
      "zh": "有，我試過了。沒有燈光，沒有聲音，什麼都沒有。",
      "ja": "うん、試したよ。ライトも音も何もない。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hmm. Maybe the battery is broken.",
      "zh": "嗯，可能是電池壞了。",
      "ja": "うーん、多分バッテリーが壊れているのかも。",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Without my phone, I feel lost. I can't play music. I can't check messages.",
      "zh": "沒有手機，我感覺迷失了。我不能聽音樂，也不能查看訊息。",
      "ja": "携帯がないと、迷子になった気分。音楽も聴けないし、メッセージも見れない。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't even see the time. Don't panic.",
      "zh": "我甚至看不到時間。別慌張。",
      "ja": "時間も見れない。慌てないで。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's take it to the repair shop. Maybe they can fix it.",
      "zh": "我們去修理店吧。也許他們能修好。",
      "ja": "修理店に持って行こう。直せるかもしれない。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The repair shop? Where? On Green Street near the cafe.",
      "zh": "修理店？在哪裡？在Green街，咖啡館附近。",
      "ja": "修理店？どこ？カフェの近くのグリーンストリートにあるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We can walk there. Okay. I have no choice.",
      "zh": "我們可以走路去。好吧，我沒辦法。",
      "ja": "歩いて行けるよ。わかった。仕方ないね。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "zh": "走吧。",
      "ja": "行こう。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Without my phone, I feel nervous. I can't check the time.",
      "zh": "沒有手機，我感到緊張。我不能看時間。",
      "ja": "携帯がないと緊張する。時間も見れない。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't listen to music. Don't worry.",
      "zh": "我不能聽音樂。別擔心。",
      "ja": "音楽も聴けない。心配しないで。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look around. The morning is beautiful.",
      "zh": "看看四周。早晨很美。",
      "ja": "周りを見て。朝は美しいよ。",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm. Maybe. But it feels strange.",
      "zh": "嗯，也許吧。但感覺很奇怪。",
      "ja": "うーん、そうかも。でも変な感じ。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Usually I just look at my screen.",
      "zh": "我通常只看螢幕。",
      "ja": "普段は画面ばかり見ている。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Try to look outside.",
      "zh": "試著看外面。",
      "ja": "外を見てみて。",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The street, the people, the shops.",
      "zh": "街道、人群、商店。",
      "ja": "通り、人々、お店。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, the smell. Wow. The bakery smells so good.",
      "zh": "喔，味道。哇。麵包店聞起來真好。",
      "ja": "ああ、匂い。わあ。パン屋の匂いがすごくいい。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes. Fresh bread. Warm bread.",
      "zh": "是啊。新鮮的麵包。溫熱的麵包。",
      "ja": "そう、新鮮なパン。温かいパン。",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Usually I just order food online.",
      "zh": "我通常只在線上訂食物。",
      "ja": "普段はオンラインで食べ物を注文するだけ。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I see real bread right here.",
      "zh": "現在我看到真正的麵包就在這裡。",
      "ja": "今はここに本物のパンが見える。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See? Real bread. Real life.",
      "zh": "看到了嗎？真正的麵包。真正的生活。",
      "ja": "見て？本物のパン。本物の生活。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The smell is sweet. Mmm. It makes me hungry.",
      "zh": "味道很甜。嗯。讓我餓了。",
      "ja": "匂いが甘い。うん。お腹がすく。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Fresh bread is always better than food on a screen.",
      "zh": "新鮮的麵包總比螢幕上的食物好。",
      "ja": "新鮮なパンは画面の食べ物よりいつもいい。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow. The bus is full of people.",
      "zh": "哇。公車上滿是人。",
      "ja": "わあ。バスは人でいっぱいだ。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes. People go to work every morning.",
      "zh": "是的。人們每天早上去上班。",
      "ja": "そうだよ。人々は毎朝仕事に行く。",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Full? You mean many people? No empty seats?",
      "zh": "滿的？你的意思是很多人？沒有空位？",
      "ja": "満員？たくさんの人？空席なし？",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Exactly. Full means no space.",
      "zh": "沒錯。滿的意思是沒有空間。",
      "ja": "その通り。満員はスペースがないこと。",
      "time": "00:02:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, I see. A full bus.",
      "zh": "啊，我懂了。滿員公車。",
      "ja": "ああ、わかった。満員のバス。",
      "time": "00:02:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I never watched this before. I always look at my phone.",
      "zh": "我以前從沒注意過這些。我總是看手機。",
      "ja": "今まで見たことなかった。いつも携帯を見ているから。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See? You can learn new things by looking around.",
      "zh": "看到了嗎？你可以透過觀察學到新事物。",
      "ja": "ほら？周りを見ることで新しいことが学べるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, wow. The trees are tall.",
      "zh": "喔，哇。樹好高。",
      "ja": "ああ、わあ。木が高い。",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The sky is so blue. Beautiful, right?",
      "zh": "天空好藍。很美，對吧？",
      "ja": "空がとても青い。きれいだよね？",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes. I usually look down at my screen.",
      "zh": "是的。我通常低頭看螢幕。",
      "ja": "うん。普段は画面を見て下を向いている。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I look up. Up is better.",
      "zh": "現在我抬頭看。抬頭比較好。",
      "ja": "今は上を見る。上を見る方がいい。",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mmm. Yes. Better.",
      "zh": "嗯。是的。比較好。",
      "ja": "うん。そうだね。いいね。",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The birds sing. The air feels fresh.",
      "zh": "鳥兒唱歌。空氣感覺很新鮮。",
      "ja": "鳥が歌っている。空気が新鮮に感じる。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I like this. Yes.",
      "zh": "我喜歡這樣。是的。",
      "ja": "これが好き。うん。",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Listen carefully. This is the real world.",
      "zh": "仔細聽。這是真實的世界。",
      "ja": "よく聞いて。これが本当の世界だよ。",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe this walk is not so bad.",
      "zh": "也許這次散步不錯。",
      "ja": "この散歩は悪くないかも。",
      "time": "00:03:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See? Without a phone, you can still enjoy life.",
      "zh": "看到了嗎？沒有手機，你還是能享受生活。",
      "ja": "ほら？携帯がなくても人生を楽しめるよ。",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe I can. Maybe I can enjoy more.",
      "zh": "也許我可以。也許我可以享受更多。",
      "ja": "たぶんできる。もっと楽しめるかも。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mmm. The smell of coffee.",
      "zh": "嗯。咖啡的香味。",
      "ja": "うん。コーヒーの香り。",
      "time": "00:03:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Strong and sweet.",
      "zh": "濃郁又甜美。",
      "ja": "強くて甘い。",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes. Fresh coffee. Do you want to stop?",
      "zh": "是的。新鮮咖啡。你想停下來嗎？",
      "ja": "そう、新鮮なコーヒー。寄る？",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm. Without my phone, I can't pay online.",
      "zh": "嗯。沒有手機，我不能線上付款。",
      "ja": "うーん。携帯がないとオンラインで支払えない。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't worry. I have cash.",
      "zh": "別擔心。我有現金。",
      "ja": "心配しないで。現金があるよ。",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, thank you. Let's sit for a moment.",
      "zh": "喔，謝謝。讓我們坐一下。",
      "ja": "ああ、ありがとう。ちょっと座ろう。",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow. It looks hot.",
      "zh": "哇，看起來很燙。",
      "ja": "わあ、熱そう。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The steam goes up.",
      "zh": "蒸氣往上升。",
      "ja": "蒸気が上がっている。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Careful. It's hot and strong.",
      "zh": "小心。它很燙也很濃。",
      "ja": "気をつけて。熱くて濃いよ。",
      "time": "00:03:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mmm. Oh, good.",
      "zh": "嗯。喔，好喝。",
      "ja": "うん。ああ、美味しい。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Better, but also smooth.",
      "zh": "更好喝，而且順口。",
      "ja": "良くなったけど、滑らかでもある。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes. Better and smooth.",
      "zh": "是的。更好且順口。",
      "ja": "そう、良くて滑らか。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Coffee gives energy.",
      "zh": "咖啡給人能量。",
      "ja": "コーヒーは元気をくれる。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Usually, I drink coffee at home with my phone in hand.",
      "zh": "我通常在家喝咖啡，手裡拿著手機。",
      "ja": "普段は家で携帯を持ちながらコーヒーを飲む。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now it feels different.",
      "zh": "現在感覺不一樣。",
      "ja": "今は違う感じ。",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Different is good sometimes.",
      "zh": "有時候不同是好的。",
      "ja": "違うのは時にはいいことだよ。",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can see people here talking, laughing.",
      "zh": "我看到這裡有人在說話、笑著。",
      "ja": "ここで人々が話したり笑ったりしているのが見える。",
      "time": "00:04:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It feels alive.",
      "zh": "感覺很有活力。",
      "ja": "生きている感じがする。",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Exactly. People. Not screens.",
      "zh": "沒錯。是人，不是螢幕。",
      "ja": "その通り。人だよ。画面じゃない。",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh. Look at the flowers.",
      "zh": "喔。看看那些花。",
      "ja": "ああ。花を見て。",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Red, yellow, pink.",
      "zh": "紅色、黃色、粉紅色。",
      "ja": "赤、黄色、ピンク。",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So bright.",
      "zh": "好鮮豔。",
      "ja": "とても鮮やか。",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, the flower shop is beautiful.",
      "zh": "是的，花店很美。",
      "ja": "そう、花屋は美しい。",
      "time": "00:04:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow. I never noticed the shop before.",
      "zh": "哇，我以前從沒注意過這家店。",
      "ja": "わあ、今までこの店に気づかなかった。",
      "time": "00:04:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Because you always look at your phone.",
      "zh": "因為你總是看手機。",
      "ja": "いつも携帯を見ているから。",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm. True. Now I see more colors.",
      "zh": "嗯，真的。現在我看到更多顏色。",
      "ja": "うん、本当だ。今はもっと色が見える。",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So many colors.",
      "zh": "好多顏色。",
      "ja": "たくさんの色。",
      "time": "00:04:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Colors make life rich.",
      "zh": "顏色讓生活豐富。",
      "ja": "色は人生を豊かにする。",
      "time": "00:04:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mmm. Yes.",
      "zh": "嗯，是的。",
      "ja": "うん、そう。",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Rich and bright.",
      "zh": "豐富且明亮。",
      "ja": "豊かで明るい。",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The water is so clear.",
      "zh": "水好清澈。",
      "ja": "水がとても澄んでいる。",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The sound is soft.",
      "zh": "聲音很柔和。",
      "ja": "音が柔らかい。",
      "time": "00:04:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes. Splash. Splash.",
      "zh": "是的。潺潺水聲。",
      "ja": "そう、チャプチャプ。",
      "time": "00:04:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, the children are so happy.",
      "zh": "喔，孩子們好快樂。",
      "ja": "ああ、子供たちはとても幸せそう。",
      "time": "00:04:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They laugh so much.",
      "zh": "他們笑得很開心。",
      "ja": "彼らはたくさん笑っている。",
      "time": "00:05:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Simple things make them happy.",
      "zh": "簡單的事讓他們快樂。",
      "ja": "シンプルなことが彼らを幸せにする。",
      "time": "00:05:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe I can learn from them to enjoy small things.",
      "zh": "也許我可以向他們學習享受小事。",
      "ja": "彼らから小さなことを楽しむことを学べるかも。",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes. Small things. Big joy.",
      "zh": "是的。小事，大快樂。",
      "ja": "そう、小さなことが大きな喜び。",
      "time": "00:05:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah. Music.",
      "zh": "啊，音樂。",
      "ja": "ああ、音楽。",
      "time": "00:05:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "A guitar. Yes.",
      "zh": "吉他。是的。",
      "ja": "ギターだ。うん。",
      "time": "00:05:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Live music.",
      "zh": "現場音樂。",
      "ja": "ライブ音楽。",
      "time": "00:05:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:05:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like the sound.",
      "zh": "我喜歡這聲音。",
      "ja": "この音が好き。",
      "time": "00:05:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Better than music on a phone?",
      "zh": "比手機裡的音樂好嗎？",
      "ja": "携帯の音楽よりいい？",
      "time": "00:05:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:05:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This sound is real.",
      "zh": "這聲音是真實的。",
      "ja": "この音は本物。",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Soft and the live.",
      "zh": "柔和且現場感。",
      "ja": "柔らかくてライブ感がある。",
      "time": "00:05:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See?",
      "zh": "看到了嗎？",
      "ja": "ほら？",
      "time": "00:05:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No phone.",
      "zh": "沒有手機。",
      "ja": "携帯なし。",
      "time": "00:05:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No problem.",
      "zh": "沒問題。",
      "ja": "問題なし。",
      "time": "00:05:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:05:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The dog runs fast.",
      "zh": "狗跑得很快。",
      "ja": "犬が速く走っている。",
      "time": "00:05:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It looks happy.",
      "zh": "看起來很快樂。",
      "ja": "楽しそうに見える。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Dogs love to play.",
      "zh": "狗狗喜歡玩耍。",
      "ja": "犬は遊ぶのが好き。",
      "time": "00:05:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The park feels peaceful.",
      "zh": "公園感覺很平靜。",
      "ja": "公園は平和な感じ。",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そう。",
      "time": "00:05:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Peaceful and calm.",
      "zh": "平靜且安寧。",
      "ja": "平和で落ち着いている。",
      "time": "00:05:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, wow.",
      "zh": "喔，哇。",
      "ja": "ああ、わあ。",
      "time": "00:05:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look at the fruit.",
      "zh": "看看水果。",
      "ja": "果物を見て。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So fresh.",
      "zh": "好新鮮。",
      "ja": "とても新鮮。",
      "time": "00:05:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes. Red apples.",
      "zh": "是的。紅蘋果。",
      "ja": "そう、赤いリンゴ。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yellow bananas.",
      "zh": "黃色香蕉。",
      "ja": "黄色いバナナ。",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Green grapes.",
      "zh": "綠葡萄。",
      "ja": "緑のぶどう。",
      "time": "00:05:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:05:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The smell is sweet.",
      "zh": "味道很甜。",
      "ja": "匂いが甘い。",
      "time": "00:05:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My mouth feels hungry.",
      "zh": "我的嘴巴感到餓了。",
      "ja": "お腹がすいた感じ。",
      "time": "00:06:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Fruits are good for you.",
      "zh": "水果對你有益。",
      "ja": "果物は体にいいよ。",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I usually buy them online.",
      "zh": "我通常在線上買。",
      "ja": "普段はオンラインで買う。",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I see the real fruit.",
      "zh": "現在我看到真正的水果。",
      "ja": "今は本物の果物が見える。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here in front of me.",
      "zh": "就在我面前。",
      "ja": "目の前にある。",
      "time": "00:06:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Touch it.",
      "zh": "摸摸它。",
      "ja": "触ってみて。",
      "time": "00:06:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Snell it.",
      "zh": "聞聞它。",
      "ja": "匂いを嗅いで。",
      "time": "00:06:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Choose it.",
      "zh": "挑選它。",
      "ja": "選んで。",
      "time": "00:06:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is better.",
      "zh": "那比較好。",
      "ja": "それがいい。",
      "time": "00:06:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Real is better.",
      "zh": "真實的比較好。",
      "ja": "本物がいい。",
      "time": "00:06:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The street is alive.",
      "zh": "街道充滿生氣。",
      "ja": "通りは生きている。",
      "time": "00:06:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So many faces.",
      "zh": "好多面孔。",
      "ja": "たくさんの顔。",
      "time": "00:06:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So many voices.",
      "zh": "好多聲音。",
      "ja": "たくさんの声。",
      "time": "00:06:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You see more without a phone in your hand.",
      "zh": "手裡沒手機，你會看到更多。",
      "ja": "携帯を持っていないともっと見えるよ。",
      "time": "00:06:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "True.",
      "zh": "真的。",
      "ja": "本当だ。",
      "time": "00:06:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today feels different.",
      "zh": "今天感覺不一樣。",
      "ja": "今日は違う感じ。",
      "time": "00:06:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Strange.",
      "zh": "奇怪。",
      "ja": "変だ。",
      "time": "00:06:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But also good.",
      "zh": "但也很好。",
      "ja": "でもいい感じ。",
      "time": "00:06:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is a lesson.",
      "zh": "這是一堂課。",
      "ja": "これは教訓だ。",
      "time": "00:06:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The world is bigger than the phone.",
      "zh": "世界比手機更大。",
      "ja": "世界は携帯より大きい。",
      "time": "00:06:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe this broken phone is a small gift.",
      "zh": "也許這壞掉的手機是一份小禮物。",
      "ja": "この壊れた携帯は小さな贈り物かも。",
      "time": "00:06:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "你好。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:06:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How can I help you?",
      "zh": "我能幫你什麼？",
      "ja": "どうしましたか？",
      "time": "00:06:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:06:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My phone is broken.",
      "zh": "我的手機壞了。",
      "ja": "携帯が壊れました。",
      "time": "00:06:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The screen is black.",
      "zh": "螢幕是黑的。",
      "ja": "画面が真っ黒です。",
      "time": "00:06:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It doesn't start.",
      "zh": "它不開機。",
      "ja": "起動しません。",
      "time": "00:06:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:06:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me see.",
      "zh": "讓我看看。",
      "ja": "見せてください。",
      "time": "00:06:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I feel nervous.",
      "zh": "我感到緊張。",
      "ja": "緊張しています。",
      "time": "00:06:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can you fix it?",
      "zh": "你能修理它嗎？",
      "ja": "直せますか？",
      "time": "00:07:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:07:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:07:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think it's only the same.",
      "zh": "我想只是電池問題。",
      "ja": "バッテリーだけだと思います。",
      "time": "00:07:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think it's only the battery.",
      "zh": "我想只是電池。",
      "ja": "バッテリーだけだと思います。",
      "time": "00:07:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I can change it.",
      "zh": "我可以換電池。",
      "ja": "交換できます。",
      "time": "00:07:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Really?",
      "zh": "真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:07:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "それは素晴らしい。",
      "time": "00:07:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It will take about one hour.",
      "zh": "大約需要一小時。",
      "ja": "約1時間かかります。",
      "time": "00:07:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One hour?",
      "zh": "一小時？",
      "ja": "1時間？",
      "time": "00:07:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:07:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We can wait.",
      "zh": "我們可以等。",
      "ja": "待てます。",
      "time": "00:07:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:07:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We can wait.",
      "zh": "我們可以等。",
      "ja": "待てます。",
      "time": "00:07:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:07:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One more hour without a phone.",
      "zh": "再一小時沒有手機。",
      "ja": "あと1時間携帯なし。",
      "time": "00:07:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One more hour to enjoy life.",
      "zh": "再一小時享受生活。",
      "ja": "あと1時間人生を楽しむ。",
      "time": "00:07:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maybe you're right.",
      "zh": "也許你說得對。",
      "ja": "たぶん君が正しい。",
      "time": "00:07:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today I saw the bakery, the flowers, the park.",
      "zh": "今天我看到了麵包店、花店、公園。",
      "ja": "今日はパン屋、花屋、公園を見た。",
      "time": "00:07:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All without a phone.",
      "zh": "全都是沒有手機的時候。",
      "ja": "すべて携帯なしで。",
      "time": "00:07:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そう。",
      "time": "00:07:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And you smiled more.",
      "zh": "而且你笑得更多。",
      "ja": "そしてもっと笑ったね。",
      "time": "00:07:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:07:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe I did.",
      "zh": "也許我有。",
      "ja": "たぶんそうだね。",
      "time": "00:07:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So many people need their phones fixed.",
      "zh": "很多人需要修理手機。",
      "ja": "多くの人が携帯を修理する必要がある。",
      "time": "00:07:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Phones break, but life doesn't stop.",
      "zh": "手機壞了，但生活不會停止。",
      "ja": "携帯は壊れるけど、人生は止まらない。",
      "time": "00:07:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "True.",
      "zh": "真的。",
      "ja": "本当だ。",
      "time": "00:07:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Life goes on.",
      "zh": "生活繼續。",
      "ja": "人生は続く。",
      "time": "00:07:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "People walk, talk, smile, even without phones.",
      "zh": "人們走路、交談、微笑，即使沒有手機。",
      "ja": "人は歩き、話し、笑う、携帯がなくても。",
      "time": "00:07:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そう。",
      "time": "00:07:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We sometimes forget that.",
      "zh": "我們有時會忘記這點。",
      "ja": "時々それを忘れる。",
      "time": "00:07:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Today is a big lesson.",
      "zh": "今天是一堂重要的課。",
      "ja": "今日は大切な教訓だ。",
      "time": "00:07:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here you are.",
      "zh": "給你。",
      "ja": "はい、どうぞ。",
      "time": "00:07:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "New battery.",
      "zh": "新電池。",
      "ja": "新しいバッテリー。",
      "time": "00:08:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It works now.",
      "zh": "現在可以用了。",
      "ja": "今は動くよ。",
      "time": "00:08:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, wow.",
      "zh": "喔，哇。",
      "ja": "ああ、わあ。",
      "time": "00:08:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The screen is on.",
      "zh": "螢幕亮了。",
      "ja": "画面がついた。",
      "time": "00:08:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My phone is alive again.",
      "zh": "我的手機又活過來了。",
      "ja": "携帯がまた生き返った。",
      "time": "00:08:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you so much.",
      "zh": "非常感謝你。",
      "ja": "本当にありがとう。",
      "time": "00:08:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're welcome.",
      "zh": "不客氣。",
      "ja": "どういたしまして。",
      "time": "00:08:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Take care of it.",
      "zh": "好好照顧它。",
      "ja": "大事にしてね。",
      "time": "00:08:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, I will.",
      "zh": "是的，我會的。",
      "ja": "はい、そうします。",
      "time": "00:08:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:08:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Strange.",
      "zh": "奇怪。",
      "ja": "変だ。",
      "time": "00:08:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have my phone again, but I don't feel the same.",
      "zh": "我又有手機了，但感覺不一樣。",
      "ja": "携帯は戻ったけど、同じ感じがしない。",
      "time": "00:08:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What do you mean?",
      "zh": "你是什麼意思？",
      "ja": "どういう意味？",
      "time": "00:08:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Before I felt lost without it.",
      "zh": "以前沒有手機我感到迷失。",
      "ja": "前は携帯がないと迷子になった気がした。",
      "time": "00:08:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I feel free with or without it.",
      "zh": "現在有沒有手機我都感到自由。",
      "ja": "今は携帯があってもなくても自由に感じる。",
      "time": "00:08:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's good.",
      "zh": "那很好。",
      "ja": "それはいいことだ。",
      "time": "00:08:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You learned something.",
      "zh": "你學到東西了。",
      "ja": "何かを学んだね。",
      "time": "00:08:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:08:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today I learned to see the world.",
      "zh": "今天我學會看世界。",
      "ja": "今日は世界を見ることを学んだ。",
      "time": "00:08:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "To smell.",
      "zh": "去聞。",
      "ja": "匂いを嗅ぐ。",
      "time": "00:08:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "To listen.",
      "zh": "去聽。",
      "ja": "聞く。",
      "time": "00:08:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "To feel.",
      "zh": "去感受。",
      "ja": "感じる。",
      "time": "00:08:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Life is bigger than a small screen.",
      "zh": "生活比小螢幕更大。",
      "ja": "人生は小さな画面より大きい。",
      "time": "00:08:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "その通り。",
      "time": "00:08:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Life is bigger.",
      "zh": "生活更大。",
      "ja": "人生はもっと大きい。",
      "time": "00:08:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:08:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The sky is so beautiful.",
      "zh": "天空好美。",
      "ja": "空がとても美しい。",
      "time": "00:08:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Orange, pink, and soft blue.",
      "zh": "橘色、粉紅色和柔和的藍色。",
      "ja": "オレンジ、ピンク、柔らかい青。",
      "time": "00:08:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そう。",
      "time": "00:08:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Evening colors.",
      "zh": "晚霞的顏色。",
      "ja": "夕方の色。",
      "time": "00:08:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I never look at the sky when I walk.",
      "zh": "我走路時從不看天空。",
      "ja": "歩いている時に空を見ない。",
      "time": "00:08:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But now it feels amazing.",
      "zh": "但現在感覺很棒。",
      "ja": "でも今は素晴らしく感じる。",
      "time": "00:08:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is the real gift.",
      "zh": "這是真正的禮物。",
      "ja": "これが本当の贈り物だ。",
      "time": "00:09:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, yes.",
      "zh": "啊，是的。",
      "ja": "ああ、そう。",
      "time": "00:09:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today I learned to look up.",
      "zh": "今天我學會抬頭看。",
      "ja": "今日は上を見ることを学んだ。",
      "time": "00:09:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not only down at my phone.",
      "zh": "不只是低頭看手機。",
      "ja": "携帯だけを見下ろすのではなく。",
      "time": "00:09:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good lesson.",
      "zh": "好課程。",
      "ja": "いい教訓だ。",
      "time": "00:09:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I feel calm, peaceful, and happy.",
      "zh": "我感到平靜、安寧和快樂。",
      "ja": "落ち着いて、平和で幸せを感じる。",
      "time": "00:09:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You know, today was special.",
      "zh": "你知道嗎，今天很特別。",
      "ja": "ねえ、今日は特別な日だった。",
      "time": "00:09:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, very special.",
      "zh": "是的，非常特別。",
      "ja": "うん、とても特別。",
      "time": "00:09:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My phone broke, but I saw the world.",
      "zh": "我的手機壞了，但我看到了世界。",
      "ja": "携帯は壊れたけど、世界を見た。",
      "time": "00:09:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I heard sounds.",
      "zh": "我聽到了聲音。",
      "ja": "音を聞いた。",
      "time": "00:09:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I smelled bread and flowers.",
      "zh": "我聞到了麵包和花香。",
      "ja": "パンと花の匂いを嗅いだ。",
      "time": "00:09:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I watched children play.",
      "zh": "我看著孩子們玩耍。",
      "ja": "子供たちが遊ぶのを見た。",
      "time": "00:09:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I felt the evening air.",
      "zh": "我感受到了傍晚的空氣。",
      "ja": "夕方の空気を感じた。",
      "time": "00:09:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And you enjoyed it.",
      "zh": "而且你享受了它。",
      "ja": "そして楽しんだね。",
      "time": "00:09:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:09:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I enjoyed it.",
      "zh": "我享受了。",
      "ja": "楽しんだ。",
      "time": "00:09:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A broken phone gave me a full day.",
      "zh": "一支壞掉的手機給了我完整的一天。",
      "ja": "壊れた携帯が充実した一日をくれた。",
      "time": "00:09:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's the meaning of today.",
      "zh": "這就是今天的意義。",
      "ja": "それが今日の意味だ。",
      "time": "00:09:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Life is not only in the phone.",
      "zh": "生活不只在手機裡。",
      "ja": "人生は携帯の中だけじゃない。",
      "time": "00:09:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Life is all around us.",
      "zh": "生活就在我們周圍。",
      "ja": "人生は私たちの周りにある。",
      "time": "00:09:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you for being with us today.",
      "zh": "謝謝你今天和我們在一起。",
      "ja": "今日は一緒にいてくれてありがとう。",
      "time": "00:09:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If you liked this story, please like, share, and subscribe.",
      "zh": "如果你喜歡這個故事，請按讚、分享和訂閱。",
      "ja": "この話が気に入ったら、いいね、シェア、登録をお願いします。",
      "time": "00:09:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Leave a comment to tell us, can you live one day without your phone?",
      "zh": "留言告訴我們，你能不能一天不使用手機？",
      "ja": "コメントで教えてください、携帯なしで一日過ごせますか？",
      "time": "00:09:58"
    }
  ]
